sequenceDiagram
  participant App as App (celular)
  participant API as Backend .NET
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant FS as Disco (.cbz)
  participant MX as MangaDex

  Note over App,API: Fase 1 — verificação de conexão
  App->>API: GET /api/health
  API-->>App: 200 OK

  Note over App,API: Fase 2 — manifest e diff
  App->>API: GET /api/sync/manifest
  API->>DB: SELECT chapters com download_status = done
  DB-->>API: lista de capítulos
  API-->>App: manifest [ { chapterId, hasFile, fileSize } ]
  App->>App: diff com library_item local

  Note over App,FS: Fase 3 — download seletivo
  loop Para cada capítulo faltando
    App->>API: GET /api/chapters/{id}/file
    API->>FS: stream .cbz (suporta Range)
    FS-->>API: bytes
    API-->>App: stream CBZ
    App->>App: grava .cbz no cartão SD
    App->>App: insere em library_item
  end

  Note over App,DB: Fase 4 — sync de progresso
  App->>API: POST /api/sync/progress [ { chapterId, lastPage, isRead } ]
  API->>DB: merge por updatedAt (last-write-wins)
  DB-->>API: ok
  API-->>App: 200 OK

  Note over API,MX: Download em background (independente do sync)
  API->>MX: GET /at-home/server/{chapterId}
  MX-->>API: baseUrl + hash + file list
  loop Páginas (respeitando 5 req/s)
    API->>MX: GET {baseUrl}/data/{hash}/{file}
    MX-->>API: bytes da página
  end
  API->>FS: salva .cbz montado
  API->>DB: download_status = done
